title: Handbook of recycled concrete and demolition waste
description:
2013 | ISBN: 0857096826 | English | 672 Pages | PDF | 24.50 MB

The civil engineering sector accounts for a significant percentage of global material and energy consumption and is a major contributor of waste material. 

The ability to recycle and reuse concrete and demolition waste is critical to reducing environmental impacts meeting national, regional and global environmental targets.
